question: How many people lived in Odense Municipality, Denmark on July 1, 2022?
asked_question_translated: Ile osób mieszkało w gminie Odense, Dania, 1 lipca 2022 r.?
answer: W dniu 1 lipca 2022 r. w gminie Odense w Danii mieszkało około 205,000 osób.
answer_translated_eng: On 1 July 2022, there were approximately 205,000 people living in the municipality of Odense, Denmark.
